loom (1.2.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Major update with file tree viewer and project navigation
  * NEW: File tree viewer with collapsible directory navigation
  * NEW: Project directory support - open entire projects with ./loom project-folder
  * NEW: File tree panel with F12 toggle shortcut
  * NEW: Context menu for file operations (new file, new folder, rename, delete)
  * NEW: Single-click file opening from file tree
  * NEW: File tree theme integration with current theme colors
  * NEW: File tree widget with modern scrollbar design
  * ENHANCED: Project opening functionality with directory validation
  * ENHANCED: Editor window layout with file tree panel integration
  * ENHANCED: Keyboard shortcuts including F12 for file tree toggle
  * ENHANCED: Configuration system with file tree toggle keybinding
  * FIXED: Scrollbar hover functionality replaced with always-visible design
  * FIXED: CSS template argument mismatch errors
  * IMPROVED: File tree navigation with expand/collapse functionality
  * IMPROVED: File tree UI with header, buttons, and modern styling
  * IMPROVED: Documentation updated with file tree features and shortcuts

